<P2>
<Pnumber>1</Pnumber>
<P2para>
<Text><?start-line?>The Local Government (Miscellaneous Provisions) Act 1982 is amended as <?new-line?>follows.</Text>
</P2para>
</P2>
<P2>
<Pnumber>2</Pnumber>
<P2para>
<Text><?start-line?>In Schedule 4, paragraph 1, sub-paragraph (1) leave out “or offering for sale of <?new-line?>any article” and insert “, offering or providing for sale of any article or service”.</Text>
</P2para>
</P2>
</P1para>
